CBRE in conjunction with Raine & Horne Commercial are pleased to offer 50 Broughton Road, Artarmon, NSW for sale via an Expressions of Interest Campaign.

Situated in Artarmon the asset represents a unique opportunity to acquire a premium fully leased office/ warehouse asset of substantial scale. 

Key Features
+ Secure net income of $646,890.57 pa (as at 1 November 2019
+ Strong 4% annual reviews
+ Committed long term tenant has been in occupation for 14 yrs
+ 47 basement car spaces
+ 0.7KM to Artarmon train station
+ 8.6Km to the Sydney CBD

Due to its proximity to the CBD, high-quality improvements and exposure to The Gore Hill Freeway, this asset has a blue-chip leasing history with Boehringer Ingelheim, Stryker and now VOIP having occupied the property over the last 25 years.

With a secure income stream and a passing net rental of $646,890.57 + GST (as at 1 November 2019), this opportunity allows for purchasers to acquire a defensive investment that will benefit from the continued strong rental growth for well located, North Shore Industrial properties.
